16:T4f4,Internal evidence clearly identifies this as a product family of ceramic femoral head components made from Biolox Delta material within the LATITUD hip replacement system by Meril Life Sciences. The brochure description confirms premium ceramic composition with excellent wear characteristics for long-term hip replacement. Entity type is confirmed as product_family representing a line of modular femoral heads available in various sizes. The implant class is definitively 'Femoral Head Component' - the ball portion of a modular hip implant that articulates with the acetabular cup. Material is confirmed as Biolox Delta, a fourth-generation alumina matrix composite ceramic known for enhanced strength and fracture resistance. No coating applies as ceramic is the bulk material. Anatomy scope is limited to hip joint. However, review is required due to: (1) missing brand field despite clear LATITUD branding, (2) no external verification available, (3) no SKU examples to validate size ranges, (4) manufacturer attribution to Meril Life Sciences cannot be verified from provided evidence alone. Classification appears accurate but requires verification of manufacturer and confirmation that LATITUD is indeed the system brand name rather than a product descriptor.7:["$","div",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-[#0A0A0A] text-white","children":[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org/\",\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"LATITUD Biolox Delta Ceramic Femoral Heads\",\"description\":\"Premium ceramic femoral heads made from Biolox Delta material. Provides excellent wear characteristics and biocompatibility for long-term hip replacement performance.\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"Meril\"},\"category\":\"Hip Replacement Components\",\"manufacturer\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Meril Life Sciences\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateOffer\",\"offerCount\":\"1\",\"lowPrice\":\"0\